criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Ability to confirm voluntary participation and agree to all trial purposes by signing
             and dating the consent form;

          -  Diagnosis of type II diabetes mellitus, and who did not reach the therapeutic goal of
             HbA1c with previous dietary, physical exercise, and previous therapies at stable doses
             within 3 months.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any clinical and laboratory findings that, in the judgment of the investigator, may
             interfere with the safety of participants;

          -  History of alcohol abuse or illicit drug use;

          -  Participation in a clinical trial in the year prior to this study;

          -  Pregnancy or risk of pregnacy and lactating participants;

          -  Known hypersensitivity to any of the formula compounds;

          -  Type 1 diabetes.
